name: The "Flower of Foresight" - Galactibles™ #18
description: Holy Poppies! Congratulations, you’ve discovered Galactible™ #18,  the “Flower of Foresight!” You’ve traveled great lengths to reach Planet Flora, where the flowers of foresight grow. Collecting this dancing flower allows you to see into the future! Your Mana has been raised by +250,000 bits! Custom beat made by Pyramid Guy! Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2021 | galactibles.com
